    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for a deep yellow pigment, either deep yellow earth containing yellow iron oxide, or a commercial mixture of yellow ocher and chrome yellow, used as a house paint color and for other purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047822/MFA Conservation and Art Material Encyclopedia Online: CAMEO (2005-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>泛指深黃色顏料的詞彙，可指含有黃色氧化鐵的深色黃土，或是商業上混合黃赭和鉻黃所得的顏料，可做為居家漆料或供其他用途。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
